1674448622.text: "In XREF_FIG, the aromatase inhibitor, letrozole, inhibits the DHEA stimulated proliferation of the MCF-7 Tet-off 3beta-HSD1 aromatase (IC 50 = 0.6 nM) and MCF-7 Tet-off 3beta-HSD2 aromatase (IC 50 = 0.9 nM) cell lines at similar rates with little change in rate observed in incubations containing doxycycline (dox), as expected for the inhibition of aromatase in these cells."
